ist Report</a> on <a href="http://bitcoinmagazine.com/10842/youve-goxed/#comment-13018">What To Do If You&#8217;ve Been Goxed</a></li></ul></div><div class="widget widget_adrotate_widgets" id="adrotate_widgets-24"><!-- mfunc --><a href="http://bitcoinmagazine.com/wp-content/plugins/adrotate-pro/adrotate-out.php?track=NDQsOCwwLGh0dHA6Ly9hZ29yYWNvbW1vZGl0aWVzLmNvbS8" target="_blank" class="ad-44" rel="nofollow" title="Agora Commodities"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/agora_gold_min.jpg" alt="The first full-service bitcoin to bullion dealer - Agora Commodities" height="250" width="300" /></a><!-- /mfunc --></div><div class="widget widget_adrotate_widgets" id="adrotate_widgets-25"><!-- mfunc --><a href="http://bitcoinmagazine.com/wp-content/plugins/adrotate-pro/adrotate-out.php?track=NTMsOSwwLGh0dHBzOi8vYml0Y29pbi10cmFkZXIuYml6Lw=" target="_blank" class="ad-53" rel="nofollow" title="Bitcoin Trader"><img src="http://bitcoinmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Bitcoin-Trader-300x250-2.gif" alt="The smart way to earn passive income online." height="250" width="300" /></a><!-- /mfunc --></div>		</div>
